{"tid":1645841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實肥媽首歌應該教識晒所有小朋友唱，變成民謠，從少就識得憎恨黑警","createTime":"2019-10-11T04:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T09:07:53.000Z","uid":18074,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26e9c3f38e988d761f339165c11c7497479074fa","tid":1645841,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:47:23.000Z","msg":"前線行動時可以唔唱，費時影響前線做嘢。但對峙時唱可以增加士氣，自己睇情況<br />\n<br />\n不過，我地應該教識其他身邊人，尤其小朋友唱，等佢地平日行街，返學，返工都隨時隨地唱，變成一首香港民謠，永遠記得黑警呢個仇恨，直至光復成功<br />\n<br />\n黑警係我地仇人！<br />\n黑警破壞香港法理！"},{"pid":"26f68239eee193247bb1e828d33db9cc9e87916d","tid":1645841,"uid":18074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"好少有一首歌可以咁hit, 仲要聽到一粒字就識得自動波唱"},{"pid":"26248681b145be6ec0ff6b3ef54fff4eeced5acb","tid":1645841,"uid":18074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"知道有人對快樂抗爭很反感，但無可否認，呢首歌凝聚到好多和理非<br />\n<br />\n所以，都係個句，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力！</span>"},{"pid":"c4df87e3084dfb9a6f39bfe61900a008acbc9b1b","tid":1645841,"uid":284264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n首個好入耳<br />\n聽兩次就記得"},{"pid":"7e4343fcf815397b2cbf84849f7b0b4479fc3178","tid":1645841,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:03:17.000Z","msg":"打爛呢個家園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81da8aa127d4137127c65e9ea27977d18fe2fdb","tid":1645841,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:26:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"530320f63dfe0bc8963200b1b1725553b4e70b76","tid":1645841,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"總之只要一 呀...啲細路就識唱"},{"pid":"a13051a0a56f66e674d0991b3752a046652c6aa6","tid":1645841,"uid":136431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"聽過細路仔玩捉依因<br />\n係分黑警同人